The paper discusses the development of cognitive radio technology and machine learning techniques for improving spectrum and energy utility of wireless communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
